headline: Skyworks Solutions (SWKS): A Fresh Look at Valuation After Sector Jitters Triggered by Texas Instruments Forecast
summary: Shares of Skyworks Solutions (SWKS) slipped 3% after a disappointing outlook from Texas Instruments. This development heightened concerns about a slowing recovery across the broader semiconductor industry and cast a shadow over sector performance. See our latest analysis for Skyworks Solutions. Against the backdrop of sector-wide jitters sparked by Texas Instruments’ outlook, Skyworks Solutions' share price has lost ground this month and year-to-date, with a 1-year total shareholder return of...
